rows.label: tlk47400164_01_msg0001
rows.name: The Cloud Ridge's as tall as ever...

rows.label: tlk47400164_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You can't see it, but the Liberalitan
Divine Beast's in there somewhere.

rows.label: tlk47400164_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If only it would just come out,
we could all live on its back...

rows.label: tlk47400164_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But unlike other countries, it's a free
Divine Beast. It just wanders around pulling
smaller island Divine Beasts along with it.
